name: Antoon Family Dental
overview:
Enjoy a lifetime of smiles when you visit our family friendly office. Dr. Sam Antoon’s dental office is located in Plano, Texas and specializes in keeping your pearly whites shining bright with our professional cosmetic and general dentistry services.

We Keep You Smiling A beautiful smile does wonders for your confidence, appearance and overall health. Our dental office keeps you smiling with personalized services and exceptional dental work. So whether you need routine dental cleanings, restorative dental services or teeth whitening, our team of professionals are here to serve you.

Family friendly cosmetic dentistry, specializing in keeping your pearly whites shining for a lifetime of smiles. Routine check ups, sealants, veneers, crowns, implants, teeth whitening, and more.
